filepages
=========

Renders django templates from the filesystem based
on request.

Installation
============

Add ``filepages`` to your INSTALLED_APPS and add a line like
this to your urls.py file:

    urlpatterns = patterns('filepages.views',
        url(r'^samples[/]*(?P<file_path>[^\.]*)/$', 'page',
            dict(base_directory_list=["samples/filepages", ])),
    )

See the test cases for more information.
